{"tid":1100680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會又派錢 果然係善堂","createTime":"2019-04-10T14:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T05:04:00.000Z","uid":34419,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"90584ab56893e0e5054eef63897031bff7104b68","tid":1100680,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"牙朗傷癒復出 強勢回歸 加上文素基治 文迪蘇傑 曼祖基奇 同 曼朱基奇 四大尖刀 可以話萬無一失 同打多人地三個無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而意甲都係被朗迷喻為五大聯賽最有挑戰性嘅聯賽 有如戰國時代中嘅泰國 力壓群雄 戰力大大拋離其他意甲七雄 可想而知祖記實力有幾強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而睇返阿積士 三流聯賽 三流球隊 仲要唔可以放領其他球隊 點同祖記打啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬會居然出祖記有平半高水 我直情懷疑佢出錯盤添 我真係諗唔到點解唔買祖記啦 真係高回報低風險 多謝馬會了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ca0e1803dfcbefa791afc63cc348ade6482baf","tid":1100680,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"支持過兒"},{"pid":"50cc7128a9962f5fa891d49a3c9611ef23730fa5","tid":1100680,"uid":208300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:40:24.000Z","msg":"已all in 祖記 等收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8273ca5124a16e3f556e3520b2fc0f1faabbfe5a","tid":1100680,"uid":204480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"直屌客勝唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddbe4d92efb252e6f49e605c6a170128423dde4","tid":1100680,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8273ca5124a16e3f556e3520b2fc0f1faabbfe5a","tid":1100680,"uid":204480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"直屌客勝唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 馬會啲精算炒咗佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef71ab56cae170a7ecbd40bff648c6ffbf90669c","tid":1100680,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b257eef9eaa57e0596d27a7dd900a830a16da620","tid":1100680,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:28:59.000Z","msg":"還我血汗錢 吸血鬼馬會"},{"pid":"983e3ad2afbcbdd4c09cdcdaec1687b9c6b5c6d4","tid":1100680,"uid":247651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"講到祖記咁勁 讓得平半仲要高水 就知有問題啦 當馬會傻架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 買左阿積屎下盤"},{"pid":"8d23276479d73eda820add6388ff12a014d56807","tid":1100680,"uid":17606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"作為朗迷買既係感情"}]}